description.narrative: This activity will build on the successful Kenya Avocado Programme and continue to increase economic and food security and support climate-smart agriculture in Kenya. The knowledge created under the activity will be disseminated to the wider sector. The objectives of the extension are to a) improve the quality of services and access to these services, and better-target these services to meet demand, and b) to improve the efficiency of the activity by improving the value for money.
